1
00:00:30,905 --> 00:00:33,074
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION AND ALL NAMES,
CHARACTERS, PLACES, AND INCIDENTS

2
00:00:33,158 --> 00:00:35,827
ARE EITHER PRODUCTS OF THE AUTHOR'S
IMAGINATION OR ARE USED FICTITIOUSLY.

3
00:00:46,212 --> 00:00:47,046
Darling.

4
00:00:48,047 --> 00:00:49,007
Honey.

5
00:00:51,926 --> 00:00:53,928
You don't know who she is, do you?

6
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,601
Let me tell you.

7
00:01:01,019 --> 00:01:03,938
Don't try anything useless. Just stop.

8
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:19,954
This was Sun-bin
when she started high school.

9
00:01:22,665 --> 00:01:23,792
But she had a different name.

10
00:01:25,251 --> 00:01:27,170
KIM SUN-BIN

11
00:01:27,796 --> 00:01:29,047
LEE LA-EL

12
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:30,340
"Lee…

13
00:01:31,007 --> 00:01:32,842
La-el."

14
00:01:53,196 --> 00:01:54,531
LEE LA-EL

15
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:58,243
Do you really want to be dragged out?

16
00:02:02,914 --> 00:02:04,082
You must be so happy.

17
00:02:04,666 --> 00:02:06,209
For now, that is.

18
00:02:11,631 --> 00:02:13,550
We're having Bo-ram's
birthday party today.

19
00:02:14,217 --> 00:02:17,428
Can we talk about this at a later time?

20
00:02:18,513 --> 00:02:20,140
Oh, Bo-ram.

21
00:02:20,723 --> 00:02:22,934
Whose daughter is she, really?

22
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,812
I'll have you removed forcefully
as you wish.

23
00:02:25,895 --> 00:02:26,729
Secretary Cha.

24
00:02:28,773 --> 00:02:29,858
It's fine, Secretary Cha.

25
00:02:30,817 --> 00:02:32,193
I'm leaving soon.

26
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,989
I mean, I saw this coming.

27
00:02:38,074 --> 00:02:41,077
I know you too well, Yoon-gyeom.

28
00:02:42,620 --> 00:02:44,706
Sharing your life with someone
for decades,

29
00:02:45,707 --> 00:02:47,792
you know everything
that's going on with them.

30
00:02:56,050 --> 00:02:57,969
Once you start to suspect,

31
00:02:58,595 --> 00:03:00,346
that feeling will never go away.

32
00:03:01,514 --> 00:03:03,641
I've dropped a little bit
of suspicion in here.

33
00:03:06,978 --> 00:03:10,106
That one drop
will start to contaminate the water,

34
00:03:11,107 --> 00:03:13,651
and it'll stain the entire cup soon.

35
00:03:15,987 --> 00:03:18,489
Just like that, your relationship
will be stained black.

36
00:03:28,291 --> 00:03:30,793
If you want your questions answered,
talk to me privately, honey.

37
00:03:33,838 --> 00:03:36,090
Real terror doesn't come
right when something bad happens.

38
00:03:38,927 --> 00:03:40,720
What's really scary…

39
00:03:42,263 --> 00:03:44,182
is feeling it creeping up on you.

40
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,980
Get up. Let's go somewhere else.

41
00:03:53,691 --> 00:03:55,193
I said I'm leaving.

42
00:03:56,653 --> 00:03:59,405
I'm busy cleaning up her mess.

43
00:04:05,036 --> 00:04:06,537
I'll get going then, honey.

44
00:04:48,204 --> 00:04:50,665
-It's me, Mr. Kang.
-What do you want?

45
00:04:50,748 --> 00:04:52,750
How dare she call you?

46
00:04:52,834 --> 00:04:54,544
She filed a lawsuit
to steal money from us!

47
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:55,670
Is this a joke or what?

48
00:04:56,963 --> 00:04:58,298
She really has no shame.

49
00:04:58,381 --> 00:05:00,758
What are you and Yoon-gyeom trying to do?

50
00:05:00,842 --> 00:05:02,427
A suit for divorce

51
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:04,387
and a countersuit for ten trillion won?

52
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:06,514
Where are your damn manners?

53
00:05:06,597 --> 00:05:08,433
You've got the entire country
in an uproar.

54
00:05:08,516 --> 00:05:10,685
You have no right to call!

55
00:05:10,768 --> 00:05:13,646
I understand how you feel, Mr. Kang.

56
00:05:14,188 --> 00:05:15,356
I'm so sorry.

57
00:05:16,441 --> 00:05:17,817
I'll just get to the point.

58
00:05:18,401 --> 00:05:19,694
We're not getting a divorce.

59
00:05:20,236 --> 00:05:21,821
I'll tell you about it in person.

60
00:05:22,530 --> 00:05:25,992
Yoon-gyeom will also tell you
that we're not getting a divorce.

61
00:05:28,077 --> 00:05:29,662
Thank you for the food.

62
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:31,539
We're going to go play in the playroom.

63
00:05:31,622 --> 00:05:33,499
-Let's go.
-Have fun, you two.

64
00:05:52,602 --> 00:05:54,270
I changed my name

65
00:05:55,354 --> 00:05:58,316
when my mother remarried
after my father passed away.

66
00:05:58,900 --> 00:05:59,984
Is that so?

67
00:06:01,652 --> 00:06:03,738
And Jin-wook is the one who remarried.

68
00:06:04,405 --> 00:06:07,867
I thought it'd hurt Bo-ram's feelings
if I told her I wasn't her real mother.

69
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,287
That was a good decision. I understand.

70
00:06:20,254 --> 00:06:21,172
But…

71
00:06:22,256 --> 00:06:24,217
there's nothing for me
to worry about, is there?

72
00:06:31,182 --> 00:06:33,935
There are times when terror grips me.

73
00:06:35,228 --> 00:06:36,145
It feels…

74
00:06:38,606 --> 00:06:42,401
like I can't breathe,
as if I'm underwater.

75
00:06:46,364 --> 00:06:47,782
It's as if I'm going to suffocate

76
00:06:48,616 --> 00:06:50,993
while trapped in an ocean of chaos.

77
00:06:52,161 --> 00:06:53,454
If I don't fight back fast,

78
00:06:55,373 --> 00:06:56,541
I'll lose.

79
00:06:59,043 --> 00:07:00,211
Are you suspicious of me?

80
00:07:01,045 --> 00:07:04,924
Is our relationship going to be stained
just like Ms. Han said?

81
00:07:28,239 --> 00:07:30,158
Like I said on the beach,

82
00:07:30,867 --> 00:07:33,244
you'll only be at ease once you've told me

83
00:07:34,579 --> 00:07:35,955
what it is that you're hiding.

84
00:07:37,874 --> 00:07:39,208
It's okay.

85
00:07:39,792 --> 00:07:41,294
Our relationship is just starting out.

86
00:07:42,170 --> 00:07:44,964
You can tell me about your past
when you feel comfortable.

87
00:08:12,992 --> 00:08:15,161
There should be
some torn papers on the table.

88
00:08:15,244 --> 00:08:16,621
Bring them to me quietly.

89
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:47,068
So-ra found out your real name?

90
00:08:47,151 --> 00:08:49,987
She also found out
that Ms. Jang approached her on purpose.

91
00:08:50,071 --> 00:08:52,448
I don't think she knows
about GEDIKS though.

92
00:08:52,532 --> 00:08:53,824
How did Mr. Kang react?

93
00:08:53,908 --> 00:08:55,284
He didn’t say much about it,

94
00:08:55,993 --> 00:08:58,079
but we need to assume
that the countdown has started.

95
00:08:58,162 --> 00:09:01,123
The real problem is Ms. Jang.
I can't reach her.

96
00:09:01,749 --> 00:09:02,708
I'll go check on her.

97
00:09:02,792 --> 00:09:04,544
No, you're in the hospital.

98
00:09:04,627 --> 00:09:05,836
I'll go.

99
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,923
I'll get the original GEDIKS contract
as soon as possible too.

100
00:09:09,632 --> 00:09:12,301
I'll ask the law firm about Ms. Jang then.

101
00:09:43,124 --> 00:09:44,500
LY EMPLOYEE AUDIT LIST

102
00:09:44,584 --> 00:09:46,127
Pass this list on to the audit department.

103
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:49,088
It has the embezzlement
and illegal trade done by LY employees,

104
00:09:49,171 --> 00:09:52,883
including Kim Yi-sak
and the resigned Jang Jin-wook.

105
00:09:52,967 --> 00:09:56,596
I could hand this over to the prosecutors
to make an example out of them.

106
00:09:57,305 --> 00:09:58,389
Yes, ma'am.

107
00:10:00,808 --> 00:10:01,642
LY, THE WORLD'S LEADING COMPANY

108
00:10:01,726 --> 00:10:03,894
-Vice President Kim.
-Yes?

109
00:10:03,978 --> 00:10:05,479
I'm Jung Myeong-ho
from the audit department.

110
00:10:05,563 --> 00:10:07,648
We've received a report
from the Strategic Planning Office.

111
00:10:08,566 --> 00:10:10,401
The Strategic Planning Office?

112
00:10:12,028 --> 00:10:14,030
What on earth are you…

113
00:10:17,992 --> 00:10:19,327
Ms. Kim?

114
00:10:21,287 --> 00:10:22,121
Ms. Kim.

115
00:10:24,332 --> 00:10:26,667
I'm not sure what this is about.

116
00:10:27,376 --> 00:10:29,170
This contract says
that you're giving up your stock shares.

117
00:10:29,253 --> 00:10:30,338
Put your fingerprint on this.

118
00:10:30,421 --> 00:10:32,506
We're desperate too.

119
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,591
Please…

120
00:10:36,260 --> 00:10:39,221
My father trusted you so much.

121
00:10:40,139 --> 00:10:42,308
We have families who depend on us.

122
00:10:42,391 --> 00:10:43,601
Get it from the inside.

123
00:10:43,684 --> 00:10:45,561
-It's okay. Just a bit more.
-It's okay.

124
00:10:45,645 --> 00:10:47,396
-It's okay.
-From the inside. It's good now.

125
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:50,441
Could we talk for a moment?

126
00:10:50,524 --> 00:10:51,400
Like I said,

127
00:10:51,484 --> 00:10:53,235
turn him over to the prosecutors
after the investigation.

128
00:10:53,944 --> 00:10:54,945
Let's go.

129
00:10:57,281 --> 00:10:58,491
Ms. Kim.

130
00:10:59,283 --> 00:11:01,410
What does LY's audit department
want from me?

131
00:11:01,494 --> 00:11:03,329
I'm in the US after retiring.

132
00:11:04,497 --> 00:11:06,165
A Retiree Summons Investigation?

133
00:11:06,248 --> 00:11:09,043
You were found to have committed
illegal and corrupt acts

134
00:11:09,126 --> 00:11:10,878
by Ms. Kim Sun-bin
of the Future Strategic Planning Office.

135
00:11:10,961 --> 00:11:13,464
If you don't cooperate, we'll send
the documents to the prosecution.

136
00:11:13,547 --> 00:11:14,382
But--

137
00:11:15,216 --> 00:11:17,593
We'll be launching
a Strategic Planning Office

138
00:11:17,676 --> 00:11:19,053
to oversee each department.

139
00:11:19,136 --> 00:11:21,472
This will be collectively referred to
as the Future Strategic Planning Office,

140
00:11:21,555 --> 00:11:24,308
and Ms. Kim Sun-bin
will be leading this office.

141
00:11:24,392 --> 00:11:26,477
So she actually reported me?

142
00:11:28,229 --> 00:11:29,230
Damn it.

143
00:11:30,147 --> 00:11:33,401
Ms. Kim canceled today's meeting too?

144
00:11:33,484 --> 00:11:35,528
She rescheduled it in a hurry
and left, sir.

145
00:11:37,029 --> 00:11:38,614
The driver works for us,

146
00:11:38,697 --> 00:11:40,699
so I can discreetly check
where she's headed, sir.

147
00:11:44,328 --> 00:11:45,287
Ms. Jang.

148
00:12:42,845 --> 00:12:44,472
What would you like me to do, sir?

149
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:47,933
-Follow her.
-Yes, sir.

150
00:13:08,537 --> 00:13:09,955
UNSEO GENERAL HOSPITAL

151
00:13:10,039 --> 00:13:11,248
What about her phone?

152
00:13:11,332 --> 00:13:13,042
Was Ms. Jang's phone missing?

153
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:14,793
Her phone was the only thing missing

154
00:13:15,503 --> 00:13:16,879
and it was turned off.

155
00:13:16,962 --> 00:13:19,340
Maybe we should
report her missing to the police.

156
00:13:20,674 --> 00:13:23,969
I'll meet with So-ra first.

157
00:13:24,595 --> 00:13:26,222
I'm the one she hates.

158
00:13:27,223 --> 00:13:29,266
She has no reason to hurt Ms. Jang.

159
00:13:30,392 --> 00:13:31,268
La-el.

160
00:13:31,352 --> 00:13:33,354
Even if you can't get
the original contract,

161
00:13:34,688 --> 00:13:37,191
I'll help you with your lawsuit
as much as I can.

162
00:13:38,067 --> 00:13:39,235
So don't do anything dangerous.

163
00:13:40,986 --> 00:13:41,820
Let's go.

164
00:13:42,947 --> 00:13:43,781
Oh goodness.

165
00:13:45,741 --> 00:13:47,660
Are you sure about being discharged?

166
00:13:48,452 --> 00:13:49,578
I need to take action

167
00:13:49,662 --> 00:13:53,040
before something like this
happens to you again.

168
00:14:10,766 --> 00:14:11,600
Follow her.

169
00:14:24,405 --> 00:14:25,906
Isn't that Mr. Kang?

170
00:14:49,513 --> 00:14:52,099
CHIEF SECRETARY SEO EUN-PYEONG

171
00:14:53,601 --> 00:14:55,019
It's been a while, Mr. Seo.

172
00:14:57,396 --> 00:14:58,230
I see.

173
00:15:01,692 --> 00:15:02,776
All right.

174
00:15:05,738 --> 00:15:06,739
Stop the car.

175
00:15:07,323 --> 00:15:08,198
Yes, sir.

176
00:15:11,327 --> 00:15:13,787
Who on earth attacked
the president's chief secretary?

177
00:15:13,871 --> 00:15:17,499
And why does nobody know
about such an incident?

178
00:15:17,583 --> 00:15:19,209
I didn't tell anyone on purpose.

179
00:15:19,835 --> 00:15:21,295
I was waiting for the right moment.

180
00:15:21,378 --> 00:15:22,963
What do you mean by that?

181
00:15:23,672 --> 00:15:28,552
I was thinking that I would
tell one of the perpetrators first,

182
00:15:29,303 --> 00:15:30,971
then threaten them with it.

183
00:15:31,055 --> 00:15:32,139
And who is that?

184
00:15:33,682 --> 00:15:36,143
I'm looking at him right now.

185
00:15:37,811 --> 00:15:39,355
You think I was behind it?

186
00:15:42,399 --> 00:15:43,984
That's ridiculous.

187
00:15:46,987 --> 00:15:48,656
How could you be so rude?

188
00:15:48,739 --> 00:15:51,992
Han So-ra, Han Pan-ro, Kim Jeong-chul,
and Kang Yoon-gyeom.

189
00:15:53,410 --> 00:15:55,412
From an outsider's perspective,
you all are the same.

190
00:15:57,081 --> 00:15:58,832
If you don't wish to be regarded the same,

191
00:15:58,916 --> 00:16:01,794
then make them stop what they're planning.

192
00:16:03,170 --> 00:16:04,838
I hope you won't be on their side

193
00:16:06,131 --> 00:16:07,841
when they get their punishment.

194
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,223
I'll be going then.

195
00:16:14,932 --> 00:16:15,766
Mr. Seo.

196
00:16:21,188 --> 00:16:22,523
I don't understand

197
00:16:23,232 --> 00:16:25,275
why you dislike me so much,

198
00:16:25,359 --> 00:16:27,569
why you're meeting with Sun-bin so often,

199
00:16:28,195 --> 00:16:29,780
or why you didn't tell anyone
about the attack.

200
00:16:29,863 --> 00:16:32,700
But one thing might explain everything.

201
00:16:35,494 --> 00:16:36,787
Do you love Sun-bin?

202
00:16:40,082 --> 00:16:42,626
Are you trying to do something
for her right now?

203
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:43,627
What if I am?

204
00:16:43,711 --> 00:16:45,504
She already chose me.

205
00:16:45,587 --> 00:16:46,880
How can you be so confident?

206
00:16:48,716 --> 00:16:50,592
How would you define your love, Mr. Kang?

207
00:16:53,512 --> 00:16:54,513
I would define my love

208
00:16:55,222 --> 00:16:56,223
as a sacrifice.

209
00:16:58,350 --> 00:17:00,602
I'm only concerned
about what I can do for her.

210
00:17:01,311 --> 00:17:04,148
I can say with confidence
that you're no competition for me

211
00:17:04,231 --> 00:17:07,818
because you suspect and stalk her,
yet you call it love.

212
00:17:08,819 --> 00:17:10,487
Loving somebody
while being suspicious of them.

213
00:17:11,447 --> 00:17:12,656
I don't know about that.

214
00:17:13,574 --> 00:17:16,785
I must say, I have a strong feeling

215
00:17:18,162 --> 00:17:20,205
that you won't be by Sun-bin's side
for too long.

216
00:17:23,167 --> 00:17:24,251
I'll be going now.

217
00:17:40,476 --> 00:17:42,603
I'll get that shirt for Mr. Kang.

218
00:17:47,858 --> 00:17:49,985
That can be a gift for Chi-gyeom.

219
00:17:50,069 --> 00:17:51,862
Get me some cuff links for them too,

220
00:17:51,945 --> 00:17:53,447
and bring me a bracelet for Soo-jung.

221
00:17:54,031 --> 00:17:54,865
Yes, ma'am.

222
00:17:56,784 --> 00:17:59,286
I used to be sick and tired
of Yoon-gyeom's family,

223
00:17:59,369 --> 00:18:02,164
but now that my mother-in-law is gone,
I might start liking them again.

224
00:18:38,158 --> 00:18:40,661
Please leave so they can talk.

225
00:18:56,552 --> 00:18:58,846
Did Yoon-gyeom kick you out already?

226
00:18:58,929 --> 00:19:00,305
What did you do with Ms. Jang?

227
00:19:00,389 --> 00:19:02,975
Why are you asking me about your mom?

228
00:19:06,478 --> 00:19:08,605
Maybe you don't know much about her
because she's your fake mom.

229
00:19:08,689 --> 00:19:09,690
Tell me where she is.

230
00:19:09,773 --> 00:19:12,860
Do you feel a sense of companionship
because you're both after money?

231
00:19:13,902 --> 00:19:15,696
Who do you think you are?

232
00:19:19,491 --> 00:19:21,994
You'll be nothing
once Yoon-gyeom loses interest in you.

233
00:19:22,077 --> 00:19:24,538
You shouldn't be so confident.

234
00:19:24,621 --> 00:19:26,123
I could tell you the same thing.

235
00:19:26,206 --> 00:19:27,374
What will you do

236
00:19:27,958 --> 00:19:30,419
if you can't win his heart back
even after I leave?

237
00:19:32,171 --> 00:19:33,547
It hasn't crossed your mind, has it?

238
00:19:35,465 --> 00:19:38,552
Why would I think about
something like that?

239
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:42,723
The perfect wife comforting her husband
who was hurt by a money chaser,

240
00:19:42,806 --> 00:19:43,724
that's my role.

241
00:19:44,308 --> 00:19:47,394
The entire country will respect me
after I put my family back together.

242
00:19:49,521 --> 00:19:51,607
That's how this lawsuit will end.

243
00:20:00,741 --> 00:20:03,744
Even after he finds out

244
00:20:04,828 --> 00:20:06,079
about Dr. Jung, your lover?

245
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:09,416
Doctor.

246
00:20:09,499 --> 00:20:10,667
Where are you?

247
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:12,920
I need a session today.

248
00:20:14,004 --> 00:20:15,005
I'll be right there.

249
00:20:15,672 --> 00:20:17,007
Where are you?

250
00:20:17,799 --> 00:20:19,676
I need to see you right now.

251
00:20:27,768 --> 00:20:29,436
DR. JUNG

252
00:20:37,653 --> 00:20:40,781
People don't know yet
that the chief secretary was assaulted.

253
00:20:41,365 --> 00:20:42,866
If people find out
that you were behind it,

254
00:20:43,867 --> 00:20:45,577
not only will you lose your husband,

255
00:20:45,661 --> 00:20:48,205
but how would you possibly live
with your head high?

256
00:21:00,759 --> 00:21:03,136
You're getting anxious
because you got exposed.

257
00:21:06,556 --> 00:21:07,724
I'll give you one day.

258
00:21:09,059 --> 00:21:12,729
Let Ms. Jang go by midnight tomorrow.

259
00:21:13,438 --> 00:21:14,898
