00:43:59,303 --> 00:44:01,764
How many times have I told you
that I need that woman?

524
00:44:01,847 --> 00:44:02,890
Bring her right now!

525
00:44:02,973 --> 00:44:04,224
I told you, I can't do that!

526
00:44:04,308 --> 00:44:06,435
She'll be the death of all of us!

527
00:44:07,519 --> 00:44:08,604
Damn it.

528
00:44:09,605 --> 00:44:11,398
She's really something else.

529
00:44:12,483 --> 00:44:14,234
She's a tough one.

530
00:44:14,985 --> 00:44:16,904
I don't think
she'll cooperate that easily.

531
00:44:20,491 --> 00:44:21,325
Mr. Han.

532
00:44:21,408 --> 00:44:24,828
These are the prosecutors
who want to be a part of the Zeus Project.

533
00:44:24,912 --> 00:44:26,038
Please take a look.

534
00:44:26,622 --> 00:44:28,040
Chief Prosecutor Kwon?

535
00:44:28,123 --> 00:44:31,085
No. He was almost indicted
on a lobbying charge.

536
00:44:34,713 --> 00:44:35,547
What?

537
00:44:38,884 --> 00:44:39,885
We've been bugged.

538
00:44:51,688 --> 00:44:53,273
Over there.

539
00:44:58,070 --> 00:44:59,154
Look under the couch.

540
00:45:05,911 --> 00:45:06,745
Move.

541
00:45:17,339 --> 00:45:18,340
Look, I found--

542
00:45:28,892 --> 00:45:29,726
Another one?

543
00:46:12,978 --> 00:46:13,979
So-ra.

544
00:46:14,771 --> 00:46:16,315
You've never fallen in love, have you?

545
00:46:16,398 --> 00:46:17,608
What will you do

546
00:46:17,691 --> 00:46:20,402
if you can't win his heart back
even after I leave?

547
00:46:21,153 --> 00:46:23,322
You should stop doing this
for your own sake.

548
00:46:30,412 --> 00:46:32,331
Why the hell would you hand over Moon-hee?

549
00:46:32,414 --> 00:46:34,625
Mr. Han and Mr. Kim

550
00:46:35,751 --> 00:46:37,044
were both enraged.

551
00:46:37,836 --> 00:46:39,254
They said to bring her no matter what--

552
00:46:39,338 --> 00:46:40,756
I need to get my husband back.

553
00:46:41,965 --> 00:46:43,926
I'll kill whoever gets in the way of it.

554
00:46:44,593 --> 00:46:45,511
Do you understand?

555
00:46:53,227 --> 00:46:56,980
Let Ms. Jang go by midnight tomorrow.

556
00:47:00,275 --> 00:47:01,944
He thinks I've never fallen in love?

557
00:47:06,740 --> 00:47:09,201
None of that matters.
If you lose your love, it's over.

558
00:47:09,952 --> 00:47:11,370
You need to take it first.

559
00:47:12,579 --> 00:47:14,998
The only thing that matters
is the final victor.

560
00:47:15,582 --> 00:47:16,583
He's mine.

561
00:47:17,876 --> 00:47:18,835
Understand?

562
00:47:19,962 --> 00:47:21,129
Yes, ma'am.

563
00:47:27,344 --> 00:47:28,178
Follow me.

564
00:48:03,338 --> 00:48:04,590
The GEDIKS contract.

565
00:48:05,465 --> 00:48:06,717
What are you doing?

566
00:48:10,178 --> 00:48:11,597
How did you get in here?

567
00:48:11,680 --> 00:48:14,224
How did you know about the safe,

568
00:48:14,308 --> 00:48:15,767
and how did you get in here?

569
00:48:15,851 --> 00:48:19,062
I would like to propose the return
of the eight-inch wafer foundry process.

570
00:48:19,146 --> 00:48:21,481
LY possesses the eight-inch
semiconductor technology

571
00:48:22,232 --> 00:48:23,900
from Mr. Lee Tae-joon,
a genius businessman

572
00:48:24,818 --> 00:48:27,571
whose company was acquired
by LY 13 years ago.

573
00:48:40,917 --> 00:48:42,502
Nobody's at home, sir.

574
00:48:43,170 --> 00:48:44,004
What?

575
00:48:57,976 --> 00:48:58,810
Ms. Jang.

576
00:49:17,829 --> 00:49:19,039
Have you located Ms. Jang?

577
00:49:19,122 --> 00:49:22,250
She's near Pan-ro's house,
but I'm not too sure.

578
00:49:22,334 --> 00:49:24,503
I got her location,
but the signal was weak.

579
00:49:24,586 --> 00:49:25,587
Okay.

580
00:49:38,266 --> 00:49:40,143
MS. KIM

581
00:49:44,106 --> 00:49:45,315
I need to go to Pan-ro's house.

582
00:49:45,399 --> 00:49:48,193
File a missing person report for Ms. Jang,
and bring the police.

583
00:50:16,388 --> 00:50:18,557
NO SIGNAL

584
00:50:20,016 --> 00:50:21,226
Ms. Jang.

585
00:50:25,981 --> 00:50:27,315
MOM

586
00:50:29,609 --> 00:50:30,444
Ms. Jang…

587
00:50:30,527 --> 00:50:32,154
The person you are
trying to reach is not available.

588
00:50:32,237 --> 00:50:34,406
Please leave a message after the…

589
00:52:47,247 --> 00:52:48,790
Understood, sir.

590
00:55:16,438 --> 00:55:17,355
KANG YOON-GYEOM
CHAIRMAN OF LY

591
00:55:52,766 --> 00:55:55,310
I guess it really is a small world.

592
00:55:56,519 --> 00:55:58,480
It's a pleasure to meet you, sir.

593
00:56:07,864 --> 00:56:08,990
I thought I lost it.

594
00:56:09,074 --> 00:56:11,159
It's very dear to me.
It's from my father who passed away.

595
00:56:11,242 --> 00:56:12,077
When I danced the tango with you,

596
00:56:12,160 --> 00:56:13,745
I felt an inexplicable connection.

597
00:56:13,828 --> 00:56:16,039
The game will never end
unless you risk everything that you have.

598
00:56:16,122 --> 00:56:18,249
I imagined that was what meeting
my twin flame would feel like.

599
00:56:18,333 --> 00:56:19,709
I'll stay with you.

600
00:56:20,502 --> 00:56:21,961
I'll be with you.

601
00:56:22,045 --> 00:56:23,213
I'm not running away.

602
00:56:24,422 --> 00:56:25,548
I just want you.

603
00:56:30,553 --> 00:56:32,097
I, Kang Yoon-gyeom, swear

604
00:56:33,181 --> 00:56:35,934
that I'll only love you
for the rest of my life.

605
00:56:36,017 --> 00:56:37,852
If there is a single lie in my words,

606
00:56:38,436 --> 00:56:40,355
then I won't be afraid

607
00:56:41,981 --> 00:56:43,399
to die.

608
00:56:45,443 --> 00:56:49,280
Can you, Kim Sun-bin,
swear in the name of God

609
00:56:51,282 --> 00:56:52,909
that you love this man…

610
00:56:55,286 --> 00:56:57,580
standing in front of you?

611
00:57:01,167 --> 00:57:02,293
Do you love me?

612
00:57:05,088 --> 00:57:05,922
Yes.

613
00:57:45,628 --> 00:57:47,297
What is all this?

614
00:57:48,006 --> 00:57:49,299
What have you done?

615
00:57:49,883 --> 00:57:52,177
How could you do this to me?

616
00:57:57,891 --> 00:57:59,517
Did you hack into my phone?

617
00:58:01,728 --> 00:58:03,313
KANG YOON-GYEOM

618
00:58:06,649 --> 00:58:08,067
Did you do it that night?

619
00:58:08,151 --> 00:58:10,361
Our first night together?

620
00:58:12,363 --> 00:58:13,490
Answer me!

621
00:58:15,533 --> 00:58:17,035
How meticulous…

622
00:58:18,495 --> 00:58:20,747
and how cruel.

623
00:58:21,539 --> 00:58:23,041
How long have you been preparing…

624
00:58:25,668 --> 00:58:27,420
to approach me like this?

625
00:58:28,129 --> 00:58:31,925
I thought you just needed some money,
but I was wrong.

626
00:58:32,634 --> 00:58:34,594
This is too terrible.

627
00:58:35,345 --> 00:58:37,472
If only you had wished for something else.

628
00:58:38,223 --> 00:58:41,351
I would have given you
everything that I have.

629
00:58:42,352 --> 00:58:43,561
I would have done

630
00:58:45,355 --> 00:58:47,065
anything for you.

631
00:58:49,484 --> 00:58:50,318
Why…

632
00:58:51,736 --> 00:58:53,196
Why did you do this to me?

633
00:59:02,956 --> 00:59:04,749
Did you want to ruin my life so badly?

634
00:59:04,832 --> 00:59:07,669
What did I ever do to you, Sun-bin?

635
00:59:08,169 --> 00:59:10,838
You should have taken my money
and my company instead!

636
00:59:10,922 --> 00:59:13,800
But you completely ruined my life!

637
00:59:13,883 --> 00:59:17,303
-Let go!
-You've stabbed me straight in my heart!

638
00:59:17,387 --> 00:59:18,221
Let go of me!

639
00:59:31,442 --> 00:59:32,485
Don't come any closer.

640
00:59:32,569 --> 00:59:33,861
Don't come near me!

641
00:59:33,945 --> 00:59:34,779
Why?

642
00:59:34,862 --> 00:59:38,116
Are you scared now after doing all that?

643
00:59:38,825 --> 00:59:40,368
Did you not expect this to happen?

644
00:59:55,883 --> 00:59:57,135
What…

645
00:59:57,218 --> 00:59:59,262
have I done?

646
00:59:59,345 --> 01:00:00,346
Are you okay?

647
01:00:01,097 --> 01:00:01,931
Are you all right?

648
01:00:02,515 --> 01:00:03,516
I'm sorry.

649
01:00:04,100 --> 01:00:05,476
-I'm sorry…
-Get away from me!

650
01:00:31,544 --> 01:00:32,962
2011, BUENOS AIRES

651
01:00:33,046 --> 01:00:36,924
SECOND SON, KANG YOON-GYEOM
CHAIRMAN OF LY

652
01:01:26,933 --> 01:01:28,851
All of you are responsible.

653
01:01:28,935 --> 01:01:32,146
Confess your crimes, and pay the price.

654
01:01:32,230 --> 01:01:34,691
Nobody has left this place alive.

655
01:01:34,774 --> 01:01:35,983
That's your punishment!

656
01:01:39,028 --> 01:01:40,113
I'm going to kill her.

657
01:01:40,196 --> 01:01:41,531
I'm going to kill them all!

658
01:01:44,450 --> 01:01:45,451
I'm so sorry.

659
01:01:46,035 --> 01:01:47,328
Let's end this, please.

660
01:01:47,412 --> 01:01:49,330
Kill them all with your own hands

661
01:01:50,248 --> 01:01:52,291
and kill yourself at the end of it all.

